data.description: Come home to your own country paradise. A spacious 5 bedroom, 3 bath home on 2 parcels totaling 4.24 acres (3.24acres is already ag exempt) outside city limits offering endless opportunities. Enjoy both the privacy of dead end street and convenient travel to Fort Worth, Weatherford or Decatur. The 2 storage buildings and large shop, already equipped with electric and spray foam insulation, gives ample room for storage or any hobby you can imagine.
